  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuizManagerArun
  questions:
  - questionText: 1, What were the workers doing?
    option1: They were cutting huge logs of wood into sm....
    option2: They were partying
    option3: ' They were watching rajinikanth movie'
    option4: They were taking nap
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 390772730a8566947b7ef32ad8c8a942, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: c1efcbe342308994d943a12982b6fe91, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 2, Who started playing with the wood?
    option1: A group of jackals.
    option2: Harry Potter.
    option3: A group of actors.
    option4: A group of monkeys.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: fa96dc49b141b9643bf890f77ebc688b, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 19ff30fc2ad5cbc4397d4f0f287b32a8, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 3, Why was  a wedge inserted halfway through the sawed wood?
    option1: To ensure that the two halves did not close up.
    option2: Because a wedge was cheaper than a hammer.
    option3: For animals to play in gap.
    option4: It was fun to experiment with placing the wedge between the halves.
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 94604322593ee6d41b2c4575d30e27e0, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: ef3c25818ee13c54badb91102e1094a7, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 4, What did the curious monkey do?
    option1: He jumped up and down on the wedge.
    option2: He was scared and ran away.
    option3: He started pulling on the wedge with all his strength.
    option4: He called for the other monkeys.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 1
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d34cf688f201bb644a9b58c3ec42d612, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 20d270bb1a151374e8ccf82c7c07f900, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 5, What happened when the monkey pulled the wedge off?
    option1: A lot of birds flew under the wedge
    option2: The two halves closed and crushed the monkey to death.
    option3: The workers came rushing to the scene
    option4: The wedges magicaly started beating him.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7146e5f60f81bf141adc435331441ba0, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: e61e7c31b84e08046a01d1eb89545a63, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 6
  - questionText: 6, What moral did Karataka tell?
    option1: He should always watch TV before going to bed.
    option2: Though vanilla is a nice flavor, strawberry is better.
    option3: He feasted on the emrald green blades of grass.
    option4: We should always speak the truth.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 877fc4625aec83642a5424f93609f529, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 75275e2fd7b56d64b888c06b15bc0ff0, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 7,Damanaka said that the king felt _____
    option1: ...joyous.
    option2: ...angry.
    option3: ...tired.
    option4: ...scared.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d5feaa8b7b9727a48ac38385da661973, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: 2c24199ec0e1df94aa95cdd04a7d7259, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: "8, How was the lion\u2019s body language?  (Select all answers
      that are correct)"
    option1: He avoided eye contact.
    option2: He was slouching.
    option3: He was stretching
    option4: He was pacing.
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 1
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
    questionAudio: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 3b34497a709b3c045b72c331920040df, type: 3}
    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: a69900a30e73f7f4bb3f48cacfd38a5f, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 4
  - questionText: 9, What did Damanaka do first after approaching Pingalaka?
    option1: He sang him a song.
    option2: He prostarted.
    option3: He danced bharatanatyam.
    option4: He hugged him.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 1
