    optionStartTime: 7
  - questionText: 10, Pingalaka agreed to talk to Damanaka beacause...
    option1: Damanaka was the son of his former minister.
    option2: he was bored and needed some company to talk to.
    option3: He was curious to know what had made his king happy.
    option4: Damanaka threatened to kill Pingalaka.
    option1IsCorrect: 1
    option2IsCorrect: 0
    option3IsCorrect: 0
    option4IsCorrect: 0
